
1. Create a training set of nodule features for classification

python create_trainset.py <out_file>
ie. python create_trainset.py data/tr.npy

2. Train classifier

python train.py <training_set_file>
ie. 
python train.py data/tr.npy

3. Execute for an sample chxr:

python lnd.py <npy_image> <left_lung_mask> <right_lung_mask>
ie. 
python lnd.py data/JPCLN001.npy data/JPCLN001-left.bmp data/JPCLN001-right.bmp

4. Evaluate on all dataset

python eval.py <real_list> <predicted_list>
ie.
python eval.py jsrt140.txt lda.txt




